    -- Proof sketch: Sum of angles in PAB, PBC, PCA is 3π.
    -- Sum of angles around P is 2π.
    -- (π - ∠APB) + (π - ∠BPC) + (π - ∠CPA) = (a+b') + (b+c') + (c+a')
    -- 3π - 2π = π.
    sorry

